{"type": "article", "id": 25926, "title": "精酿啤酒包装", "description": "", "date": "2016-04-25T06:59:11Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 49, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607104404xYsN07qdePIlRp9y.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是 <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://braind.am/\">Braind</a> 为亚美尼亚共和国首都埃里温（Yerevan）的 Dargett Brewery 精酿啤酒所设计的包装。Logo 的灵感来源于公元六世纪前的巴比伦地图，圆环所代表的 Bitter River 与品牌名结合，和极具标识性的图案一起巧妙地传递出酿酒传统与工艺仍在延续的概念，复古又清新，让人眼前一亮。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104402q2VKZWgA3esMhimO.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104402iQm5jG4O1AxINr92.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104403mpM0vfr5Wk34GlXC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104403Kf9BQn8g7aXDvc4b.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}